## Example Repo (for testing)

A minimal Flask app is included at `devopsify-example-app/` to test DevOpsify end to end.

### Run the example

```bash
# push devopsify-example-app to your GitHub first, then:
devopsify deploy --repo https://github.com/<your-username>/devopsify-example-app
```

DevOpsify will detect:

| Signal | Detected Value |
|---|---|
| Language | Python |
| Entry point | app.py |
| Port | 5000 |
| Secrets | PORT, APP_ENV, SECRET_KEY |
| DB | none |

### Expected output

```
devopsified-output/
└── devopsify-example-app/
    ├── Dockerfile
    ├── docker-compose.yml
    ├── README.md
    ├── k8s/
    │   └── ...
    ├── terraform/
    │   └── ...
    └── .github/
        └── workflows/
            └── deploy.yml
```

After deploy, app is available at the minikube service URL printed in the terminal.

---

## Monitoring

After deploy, DevOpsify automatically deploys Prometheus + Grafana into the cluster.

| Service | URL | Credentials |
|---|---|---|
| Grafana | http://localhost:3000 | admin / admin |
| Prometheus | http://localhost:9090 | — |

Port-forward is started automatically. Both are destroyed on cleanup.

---

## Secrets

- Detected from `.env.example` in your repo
- Values collected via hidden input (never printed)
- Injected directly into the cluster via `kubectl create secret`
- Never written to any file, ever

---

## Supported Languages

| Language | Detection Signal |
|---|---|
| Python | `requirements.txt` exists |
| Node.js | `package.json` exists |

---

## What Is Not Supported (v1)

- Languages beyond Python and Node.js
- Monorepos or microservices
- KMS / Vault / external secret managers
- Multi-region deploys

---

## Architecture

```
GitHub Repo
    │
    ▼
┌─────────┐     ┌────────────┐     ┌───────────────┐
│  Clone  │────▶│  Detect    │────▶│ Generate Files│
└─────────┘     └────────────┘     └───────┬───────┘
                                           │
            ┌──────────────────────────────┤
            │                              │
            ▼                              ▼
     ┌─────────────┐              ┌──────────────────┐
     │   minikube  │              │   AWS EKS (cloud)│
     │─────────────│              │──────────────────│
     │ docker build│              │ terraform apply  │
     │ kubectl apply│             │ ECR push         │
     │ port-forward│              │ kubectl apply    │
     └──────┬──────┘              └────────┬─────────┘
            │                              │
            └──────────────┬───────────────┘
                           │
                           ▼
                ┌────────────────────┐
                │ Prometheus+Grafana │
                │ HPA autoscaling    │
                │ Secrets injected   │
                └────────┬───────────┘
                         │
                         ▼
                ┌────────────────────┐
                │   Demo running ✔   │
                │   Auto-destroy     │
                └────────────────────┘
```

